Task 2 - Digital Portfolio
In this task , you will the GitHub , LinkedIn and Kaggle Account .
• GitHub : GitHub is a web-based platform that hosts Git
repositories, providing a cloud-based interface for developers
to store, manage, track, and collaborate on code projects .
• LinkedIn : LinkedIn is a professional application used by about
1 billion peoples over 200 countries .This is a platform where
you share your professional achievement , seeking for jobs
here, sharing resume b/w the companies and the employee
seeking for jobs etc..
• Kaggle : Kaggle is an online community and platform for data
science and machine learning, acquired by Google in 2017. It
allows users to find datasets, participate in competitions to
solve complex problems, and use cloud-based code notebooks
(similar to Google Colab) to build models. It is widely used for
learning, building portfolios, and networking.
